HOW TO RUN
--------------
1. Make sure you have Google Chrome or Internet Explorer 9 or 10 installed.
2. Uncompress the tarball into it's own directory. Make sure the file hierarchy is not damaged.
3. Open index.html in the browser of your choice (of course, one of 2 listed in Step 1).
4. Click things. Enjoy the media.


Live demo can be seen at index.vishnurajeevan.com/jarvis
